entry.title: 开启我的博客之旅
entry.content: Welcome to Coder LiXinHua’s Blog!This is my first blog.Thank for you coming,and thank for your support.They are the energy to encourage me to move forward.From now on, I will update my blog regularly.I will record my learning knowledge here. Truth优秀的人，不是不合群，而是他们合群的人里面没有你
